Additionally, discussions about the "SUAPP" participation opportunity in their blogs, Websites, Forums and Pages/Thread. Removing an article in the middle of ICO crowdsales will disqualify you. Additionally, SUAPP promotional images must be of different sizes and must be posted on blogs, Websites, Forums and Social media. Keep the image until the end of the ICO crowdsales. Join our Facebook, Telegram, Reddit, Medium and Twitter today. Be a part of decentralized idea sharing and rewards blockchain community, Payment will be paid along with all other bounties. Note: All bounty Payments will be Issued after End of ICO crowdsale and Token Distribution.
